{"url": "https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/kate-hudson-shaves-her-head_us_59788fd9e4b0a8a40e841654", "text": "The \u201cAlmost Famous\u201d star shaved her head for an upcoming role in the film \u201cSister,\u201d which is written and directed by Sia. Hudson debuted her buzzcut on the Los Angeles set Tuesday, but it is believed she cut her hair last month.\n\nKate Hudson has ditched her signature blond locks and joined the ranks of method actresses like Charlize Theron and Demi Moore.\n\nAlthough details of the project have been kept under wraps, \u201cSister\u201d is reportedly a musical and also stars Sia\u2019s prot\u00e9g\u00e9, Maddie Ziegler. Hudson\u2019s stepdad, Kurt Russell, leaked some information in a recent interview with Harry Connick Jr.\n\n\u201cI don\u2019t know if, cat out of the bag, if the deal\u2019s not made or anything, but I think that she\u2019s gonna do this musical that Sia is going to direct,\u201d he said. \u201cThat sounds fantastic, so I hope that happens.\u201d\n\nHudson did post a photo with Ziegler on July 12, writing, \u201cDance rehearsal with this bundle of excellence! \ud83d\udc83\u2764\ufe0f .\u201d\n\nNow we understand why she cropped half her head out of the photo ...", "images": ["https://www.facebook.com/tr?id=1887969784608635&ev=PageView&noscript=1", "https://amp.assets.huffpost.com/assets-1123f83be23039b1d729cd5de964f5e0/images/snapchat/huffpost-in.png", "https://img.huffingtonpost.com/asset/5f0d7c60220000dc09386f1e.jpeg?ops=150_150", "https://amp.assets.huffpost.com/assets-1123f83be23039b1d729cd5de964f5e0/images/logos/HuffPost-left.svg", "https://amp.assets.huffpost.com/assets-1123f83be23039b1d729cd5de964f5e0/images/logos/HuffPost.svg", "https://img.huffingtonpost.com/asset/5f0d764a250000cb09c29b09.png?cache=GsNto4BNEK&ops=150_150", "https://img.huffingtonpost.com/asset/5f0c38912700002b09e66a9f.jpeg?ops=150_150", "https://img.huffingtonpost.com/asset/5f0d58d2250000e909c29aee.jpeg?cache=3kpFcMBA6k&ops=150_150", "https: